# Summary
This documentation explains how to set up webhooks for custom monitors in Amplitude, allowing automated messages to be sent to specified endpoints when KPIs change, enabling real-time integration with other applications without API polling. The page details the step-by-step process for creating and configuring webhooks in the Organization settings.

